<P>
 Kenetech Completes Financing for Two Energy Projects: The company said Nations 
Financial Capital Corp. of Stamford, Conn., has acquired a 25% stake in two 
Kenetech Windpower projects in California and Minnesota. San Francisco-based 
Kenetech Corp., which provides electric-power products and services, in January 
