<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 / THE FIRST ROUND; SPOTLIGHT; RUMOR OF THE DAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JULIE CART 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Maradona's positive test for stimulants came as no surprise to those who 
observed his quick weight loss -- 26 pounds in a month -- and attributed it to 
chemical help. JULIE CART 
</P>
