<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 / THE FIRST ROUND; SPOTLIGHT; TWICE AS GOOD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MIKE DOWNEY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Brazilian journalist to Alexi Lalas: "What percent of chance do you think 
USA has to defeat Brazil?" 
</P>
<P>
 Lalas: "What percent? A 100% chance. USA has a 100% chance to defeat Brazil, 
same as Brazil has a 100% chance to defeat the USA." 
</P>
<P>
 Brazilian journalist: "Ah, I see." 
</P>
<P>
 Lalas: "Got that? That's 200%." MIKE DOWNEY 
</P>
