<HEADLINE>
<P>
TICKETS AVAILABLE FOR THREE GAMES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A limited number of tickets to the final, semifinal and third-place World Cup 
games at the Rose Bowl will go on sale Tuesday at 9 a.m. 
</P>
<P>
 The semifinal game is Wednesday July 13, the third-place game is Saturday July 
16 and the championship game is Sunday July 17. 
</P>
<P>
 Tickets can be purchased by calling World Cup Ticketing at 1-800-769-1994 or 
in person at the Rose Bowl, the Forum, The Pond of Anaheim, the Sports Arena 
and the Pantages Theater on Hollywood Boulevard. 
</P>
