<P>
 Mission Energy Co.: The company's first power plant in Florida begins 
commercial operation today, a month ahead of schedule. 
</P>
<P>
 The plant, a 150-megawatt, gas-fired cogeneration facility in Polk County, 
will sell electricity to Florida Power Corp. and steam to Coca-Cola Foods and 
Todhunter International Inc. 
</P>
<P>
