<P>
 Stationery -- In Thursday's Life & Style, some of the photo captions with "The 
Paper Chase" were incorrect. The picture under the headline "More Style Than 
Money" shows a green marbleized pen ($25), Noteworthy, Beverly Center. The 
picture under the headline "Old Meets New" shows Noteworthy's filigree pen 
($40), inspired by Montblanc's famous spider design. 
</P>
